1) Standard configuration
  ------------------------

./configure
make


2) Configuration options
  -----------------------

Target processor
 - posibilities: ST231 (default), ST220
 - option: --enable-st220

Subnormals support
 - posibilities: no (default), yes
 - option: --enable-subnormals

Rounding modes
 - posibilities: nearest only (default), all IEEE modes
 - option: --enable-all-rnd-modes

